N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 366.1 - Applicability of office regulations

State Regulations
CAP is operated as part of a district's Family Assistance
program. As such, CAP participants are subject to all the regulations of this

Title governing FA, unless otherwise specified in this Part. Notes
